summary: god I can’t stop staring at and thinking about those Charizard gifs.... not just because they’re adorable, but just like... the...
body: god I can’t stop staring at and thinking about those Charizard gifs…. not just because they’re adorable, but just like… the body language is SO good!! his almost human-like expression of surprise before adopting a submissive posture, all wide-eyed and trying to look as non-threatening as possible… and the level of detail in the modeling and texture and animation is so good!!! The skin of his belly folds when he bends over! He has nicitating membranes!! Most people might not even actively notice those details but they’re THERE and they go SO FAR to make it feel like Charizard (and really every Pokémon in this movie, they’re all so good) is a real creature that could be physically interacted with and it’s so good
